      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i've had anxiety before but this feels a bit different. it's just like a stabbing sensation in one spot though. u think i should really go to a hospital or is it probably just gas or something from the flight? i'm in dubai and it's super late so i don't really want to deal with an ER if i don't have to.",
