      "content": "Stabbing sensations are always a sign that something needs a quick, expert look, and gas is a weak excuse for real pain. Since you're in Dubai, you should absolutely find a local urgent care center or a walk-in clinic right now. For immediate relief, try a very small dose of an over-the-counter anti-inflammatory, like Ibuprofen, and then get yourself seen by a professional.",
